title: Rain and diesel spillage hit Russian practice
text: Oct. 10, 2015 | 12:06 AM Rain and diesel spillage hit Russian practice Williams Formula One driver Felipe Massa of Brazil drives during the second practice session ahead of the Russian F1 Grand Prix in Sochi, Russia October 9, 2015. REUTERS/Maxim Shemetov Share Reuters   * * A version of this article appeared in the print edition of The Daily Star on October 10, 2015, on page 13. Recommended
